com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs

Class InMemoryOutput<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.Output<O,List<List<O>>>
      • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs.InMemoryOutput<O>
  • Type Parameters:
    O - type of values accepted by this output
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class InMemoryOutput<O>
extends Output<O,List<List<O>>>
    An Output that collects all values in memory and returns them on finish(java.util.Collection<? extends com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.OutputWriter<O>>). Don't use this unless the entire output is small enough to fit in memory.
    Author:
    ohler@google.com (Christian Ohler)
